Thursday 24th July 2014 ITV4
7pm to 8pm Highlights

Highlights of stage 18 another short mountain stage today. After two catagory three climbs, the riders start the ascension of the legendary Col du Tourmalet, a climb that should act as a springboard before the finish up the Hautacam. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary by Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting the reporter at the roadside.
